      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARA'S MILENA (1) did a good job to finish third last time out over 520m at Q Parklands (30.15) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot. This looks easier and expected to bounce back. PILTON VIEW (4) is a consistent dog overall, in the frame at two of nine starts including four wins but missed the frame latest when fourth (30.89) over 550m at this track. Meets a moderate line up and should run well. ART OF DECEPTION (2) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by a neck at this track in a handy 30.80 beating Oliver Go. Ran the fastest time on the program in her latest win. Leading chance again. HARA'S MILLY (3) missed the frame latest (35.26) when sixth over 600m at Q Parklands in a Grade 4/5. Already a winner from this draw.",
